<HL>
   Imperial Oil to Sell
   Refining Assets
   On Canada's Coast
   ----
   By Suzanne McGee
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/16/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C15
</SO>
<CO>
   IMOA U.UMA IMO.A XON
</CO>
<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
